HEADWORD: Atriplex
<hw>Atriplex</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a genus of plants of the goosefoot
family (<fam>Chenopodiaceae</fam>); its members include species called
<stype>orach</stype> and <stype>saltbush</stype>.</def>⟦br⟧
